edBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:08:21.000Z","msg":"紅色旺一旺佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"新一年祝腸哥搵大錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早日脫離戴綠帽嘅傷痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef95920ae01a50ac98dc47202adee8de3a3f4283","tid":2405152,"uid":170988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />許さん=不可原諒"},{"pid":"935471201a3ccf7c223a08b7c60ccf1f61aaec80","tid":2405152,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9600e3ac414b89dc40143521d007a46cc39e3bc","tid":2405152,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"俗話說「陳林滿天下」，但在百家姓中，意想不到的姓氏也是不少，撇開常見之外，有幾個姓氏，真的讓人猜想不到，甚至一輩子可能都不會遇見這樣姓氏的朋友，而且還有可能因為時代，導致姓氏讓人尷尬害羞。首先是「睪」，在現代這是個難以啟齒的字眼，但是在古代並沒有現在的含義。<br />\n<br />\n睪又通皋，原本意思是向上天或是祖先祭祀，希望來年風調雨順穀物豐收。而睪姓則最早來自於上古時期，當時在東夷部落有一位名叫皋陶的首領，此人本領非凡，甚至還與堯、舜、禹等三人被稱為「上古四聖」。<br />\n<br />\n另一個是「操」，可能很多人的第一反應會想到是一句罵人的話。如今有這個姓的人也不多，但是操姓在古代可是不容小視的大姓，因為此姓氏的祖先是曹操。曹魏末年，司馬一族大肆迫害曹氏子孫，為了保存血脈，曹氏後人不得不改名逃亡他鄉，其中就有一部分改名為操。除此之外，該姓來源還有一種說法，那就是這本是商朝的貴族姓，由君主賞賜得名，當時被賜名人的人可是無比地榮幸。目前操姓主要分布在江西和安徽一帶，分布比較集中。根據統計，全中國大約有12萬人是這個姓氏。<br />\n<br />\n還有就是「屍」，中國人凡事都喜歡討個好彩頭，取名也是如此，都會往吉利的方向去，但「屍」這麼一個晦氣的字眼，如何才能取得好的名字呢？據史冊記載，屍姓源自於東周時期，有一位士大夫受封了一塊名為「屍」的封地，而他的後人們則以此封地為姓，一直傳到了今天。如今這些姓氏的後人大多生活在中國的甘肅地區，但大部分人並沒有遇見過該姓的後人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:11:37.000Z","msg":"吳廣德<br />\n吳好提"},{"pid":"bda0969d16f1cd3219c53c78df7401e2a05339ba","tid":2405152,"uid":279513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93c81e86ac375b8a757fada13031aa6beca6e7cd","tid":2405152,"uid":52605,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"喺一間公司/機構太特別嘅姓冇咩好處<br />\n容易比人點相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"Neville Ng"},{"pid":"2c54ff8e9e8fcac45d6095015211b214279a158d","tid":2405152,"uid":114023,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eea0ba68319edc0c511943b8f3c81c50a7d8f925","tid":2405152,"uid":31521,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"史廖林白蔡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdD9MT1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdD9MT1.png&h=019498e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16c96e4f6981369def6c978c9fc83fcf65e8f9e0","tid":2405152,"uid":11081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9198ad46febdb64c4b375a8c8cd64cd83546f66","tid":2405152,"uid":261849,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"變左施 高 曹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:01:19.000Z","msg":"曹操=操操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4934afb05590ee807a477becb28434e94c0814","tid":2405152,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef95920ae01a50ac98dc47202adee8de3a3f4283","tid":2405152,"uid":170988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />許さん=不可原諒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadcce6acac9c481a08498b7b81e59739080d992","tid":2405152,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef95920ae01a50ac98dc47202adee8de3a3f4283","tid":2405152,"uid":170988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset